      <title>津巴布韦将恢复曾被指责为货币崩溃的移动货币服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/zig-usd-zimbabwe-to-revive-mobile-money-service-once-blamed-for-currency-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦将允许移动货币代理商再次运营，以促进其新的黄金支持货币的使用。移动货币代理商曾被指责助长了现已不复存在的津巴布韦元的崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/zig-usd-zimbabwe-to-revive-mobile-money-service-once-blamed-for-currency-crash</guid>
